ali\u2019 and \u2018Millionaires Row\u2019\u3002\u8fd9\u91cc\u62e5\u6709\u5df4\u5398\u5c9b\u6700\u7f8e\u4e3d\u7684\u6c99\u6ee9\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u996d\u5e97\u90fd\u8bbe\u6709\u5a5a\u793c\u4eea\u5f0f\u7684\u670d\u52a1\uff0c\u6709Legal Wedding Package\u548cSimple &amp; Sweet Package\u7684\u533a\u522b\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u4f9d\u7167\u6bcf\u5bf9\u65b0\u4eba\u7684\u9700\u6c42\u800c\u505a\u9009\u62e9\uff0c\u4e3e\u529e\u5b8c\u5a5a\u793c\uff0c\u8fd8\u53ef\u4ee5\u987a\u4fbf\u5ea6\u871c\u6708\u3002</p><br><br><p><strong>\u25b2 Tanjung Rhu beach</strong></p><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a00de70a90c402aa255e1b9e229a0dea_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a00de70a90c402aa255e1b9e229a0dea_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a00de70a90c402aa255e1b9e229a0dea_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a00de70a90c402aa255e1b9e229a0dea_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/3ac1e7565d0d1e47a28f6094545f8f38_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/3ac1e7565d0d1e47a28f6094545f8f38_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/3ac1e7565d0d1e47a28f6094545f8f38_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/3ac1e7565d0d1e47a28f6094545f8f38_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/14a7ac3ef37eef03b15fd6367fedf8c6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/14a7ac3ef37eef03b15fd6367fedf8c6_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.